              "description": "The email has been reviewed and accepted as-is. The human explicitly or implicitly expresses approval, indicating that no changes are needed.\n\nExample phrases include:\n\n\"Sieht gut aus.\"\n\"Kannst du so weiterschicken.\"\n\"Genehmigt.\"\n\"Keine Änderungen nötig.\"\n\"Super.\""
            },
